== 其它 ==
* 科學家認為[[1954年|1954年]]的这一天是[[历史上最平淡无奇的一天|历史上最平淡无奇的一天]]，在这天没有发生任何大事，也没有大人物死亡<ref>{{cite news|author=ALEX EICHLER|title=Was April 11, 1954 the Most Boring Day in History?|url=http://www.theatlanticwire.com/features/view/feature/Was-April-11-1954-the-Most-Boring-Day-in-History-2639|accessdate=2010-11-30|newspaper=The Atlantic|date=November 29, 2010|archive-date=2010-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101202012249/http://www.theatlanticwire.com/features/view/feature/Was-April-11-1954-the-Most-Boring-Day-in-History-2639|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://article.yeeyan.org/view/141320/155328 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-04-15 |archive-date=2012-05-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120522014938/http://article.yeeyan.org/view/141320/155328 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

